'''Quintin Bartog''' was a [[Crime lord/Legends|crime lord]] who once resided aboard [[Zirtran's Anchor/Legends|''Zirtran's Anchor'']] in the ''[[Laughing Sullustan]]'' in [[Sector Delta]]. He disappeared mysteriously along with all other life forms aboard the station when it vanished mysteriously, only to reappear lightyears away.<ref name="Zirtran's Anchor">{{JournalCite|5|Zirtran's Anchor (article)}}</ref>

